com.b2international.snowowl.snomed

Interface Concept

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Annotatable, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, Component, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Inactivatable, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConceptImpl

    public interface Concept
extends Component, Inactivatable, Annotatable
    Representation of a clinical idea with a unique SNOMED CT identifier.

    The following features are supported:

    • Definition Status
    • Outbound Relationships
    • Inbound Relationships
    • Descriptions
    • Exhaustive
    • Fully Specified Name
    • Primitive

    See Also:
    SnomedPackage.getConcept()
